    // Problems
    'casos.problems.backPain.title': 'Back and neck pain',
    'casos.problems.backPain.description': 'One of the most frequent reasons for consultation. Lumbar pain, cervical contractures, stiffness, or that feeling of "carrying the world on your back".',
    'casos.problems.stress.title': 'Stress and anxiety',
    'casos.problems.stress.description': 'The body enters "permanent alert" and doesn\'t know how to disconnect. Many people arrive with palpitations, chest tension, insomnia or feeling short of breath.',
    'casos.problems.digestive.title': 'Digestive problems',
    'casos.problems.digestive.description': 'When the digestive system gets blocked, it\'s not just hard to digest food —also emotions and daily life.',
    'casos.problems.migraines.title': 'Migraines and cranial tension',
    'casos.problems.migraines.description': 'Recurring head pain, photophobia, sounds that bother or extreme fatigue. The mind can\'t flow when the body is tense.',
    'casos.problems.lowEnergy.title': 'Lack of energy or low performance',
    'casos.problems.lowEnergy.description': 'When everything is difficult, when you wake up tired or feel your body "doesn\'t respond". It\'s not laziness —it\'s lack of internal regulation.',
    'casos.problems.hormonal.title': 'Hormonal problems or irregular cycles',
    'casos.problems.hormonal.description': 'The female body speaks through cycles. When there\'s pain, imbalance or exhaustion, it means something isn\'t in balance.',
    'casos.problems.sleep.title': 'Difficulty sleeping',
    'casos.problems.sleep.description': 'The mind doesn\'t stop, neither does the body. Rest is essential to regenerate and maintain physical and mental health.',
    'casos.problems.recovery.title': 'Recovery after an injury',
    'casos.problems.recovery.description': 'After a fall, operation or accident, the body can remain with stiffness or fear of movement.',
    'casos.problems.backPain.symptom1': 'Stabbing pain or constant tension in the lower back or neck',
    'casos.problems.backPain.symptom2': 'Difficulty turning the neck or lifting the arm',
    'casos.problems.backPain.symptom3': 'Fatigue after sitting or standing for a long time',
    'casos.problems.backPain.symptom4': 'Feeling of pressure on shoulders or head',
    'casos.problems.backPain.cause1': 'Maintained postures and poor ergonomics',
    'casos.problems.backPain.cause2': 'Accumulated emotional stress',
    'casos.problems.backPain.cause3': 'Lack of movement and sedentary lifestyle',
    'casos.problems.backPain.cause4': 'Blocked or shallow breathing',
    'casos.problems.backPain.treatment': 'We work with therapeutic massage, myofascial release, Kinesiology to find the deep cause (stress, joint or visceral blockage), and postural re-education techniques (Feldenkrais).',
    'casos.problems.backPain.results': 'Many people notice immediate relief and more mobility after the first session. Over time, the body relearns to support itself with less effort and more fluidity.',
    'casos.problems.stress.symptom1': 'Constant thoughts and mental loop',
    'casos.problems.stress.symptom2': 'Difficulty relaxing or sleeping',
    'casos.problems.stress.symptom3': 'Neck pain, jaw tension, morning fatigue',
